sources.title: Lake City (Full Movie) Crime Drama Drugs.  Sissy Spacek, Dave Matthews, Troy Garity, Rebecca Romijn
sources.description:
A desperate young man, on the run from a dangerous drug dealer, returns to his mother, years after a family tragedy drove them far apart, to hide. However, his old and new life are about to collide.

Directed by Hunter Hill | Perry Moore
2008
Starring:
Sissy Spacek
Drea de Matteo
Rebecca Romijn
Troy Garity
Dave Matthews
Keith Carradine
Jason Davis
Barry Corbin

Shot in Virginia.  Premiered at the 2008 Tribeca Film Festival

#drama
